{"tid":424054,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新版討論區app封測正式展開🤘","createTime":"2017-10-04T11:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T17:03:39.000Z","uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"974873c6c7622ff58217e0f246f76e0052955306","tid":424054,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早前我們向Apple提交新版討論區app封測申請，現獲准展開測試，Android與iOS 新版討論區app已同步發放。所有申請封測的會員將直接從電郵或PM收到新app下載通知，毋須再通過PM另行確認：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n- iOS用戶：請先下載TestFlight程式，當收到來自Apple的通知電郵之後，點擊電郵內相關連結即可下載安裝新app。<br />\n- Android用戶：收到來自高登公關（會員ID：586349）的通知PM，內含<br />\n新app apk檔下載連結。<br />\n<br />\n至於有興趣參與封測的會員仍可向高登公關提交申請。截至目前為止，我們總共收集到過千個申請，衷心感謝各位踴躍支持。在此祝大家中秋節快樂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n煩請各位於此post內集中回報新版討論區app問題，至於有關功能上的建議我們亦會先收集，再安排日後加入更新。<br />\n<br />\n*新版app有部分設計尚未屬最終版本（包括黑色背景模式），預計推出正式版時會完成。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牙租😘😘😘😘"},{"pid":"222b1e6389c65fa3bd11262f0ed6678ff7249622","tid":424054,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:27:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6a5924d2f567ab618363d2eed18ab7e2d3a1b5a","tid":424054,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"屌拿星以為個email係垃圾剷撚左"},{"pid":"f228b97c1f2068a891b851123de7616b389a33e1","tid":424054,"uid":7090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"用緊新app了"},{"pid":"4ba18ddbf0953b72a06b011d209321c46408090d","tid":424054,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌拿星以為個email係垃圾剷撚左</blockquote><br />\n😰"},{"pid":"6cd3ea5413ce57c46b485b441f8764908588640a","tid":424054,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"之前收到pm試近 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b231e1141a0a361f83d206270561dfeac89d2dd5","tid":424054,"uid":6624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"揾人做免費TESTING<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f646041a6097424803ea04fbf2df529d4166918","tid":424054,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"回家啦"}]}